channel.title: InFecTionX
channel.description:
[center]InFecTedX[/center] [center]LeT The HaXx BeGin[/center] InTroducTion Let me start off by saying that Project-InFecTion is a project that I have been working for a long time. It however was never released to the public. I have been working on this server alone as I have not found anyone capable to help me. Now, I am not the best coder in the world, so I do need help in making Project-InFecTion into the server I have dreampt about. So I come here today to as you guys to help me into making Project-InFecTion into the "Perfect" server. [center][img]http://img853.imageshack.us/img853/8639/informationf.jpg[/img][/center]
-Hand Cannon working 80% -All spirit shields working perfectly with correct effects. -Torva armour working perfectly with correct effects. -All specials including Vls, Swh, Claws, Dbow, etc.. are 100% -Combat is amazing. -Soulsplit actually working. -Turmoil working perfectly. -FullScreen. -New Rs trade interface. -Real Karosi Spec 100%. -All basic minigames, Jad, Fight Pits, Duel arena, etc.. -Switching is perfect. --Gameframe Toggling --Grand Exchange --Improved Combat --Whip Coloring
Will Be added:
-Bounty Hunter (fully working.) -Donator Zone / Staff Zone. -Player Panel. -Custom Jframe. -Zombie minigame.
[center][img]http://img402.imageshack.us/img402/3238/mediazf.jpg[/img][/center] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OT8dps6mLc0[/youtube] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vx2WmasqdL4[/youtube] Spots Taken/Available:
Source Coders- 1/3 (Me) Client Coders- 0/2 Web Designer- 1/1 (Joshua) GFX Designer- 2/3 (Me)(Joshua) Hoster- 1/1(Ap0c4lyps3)
If you would like to join this project please fill the information below corresponding to your position choice. Client Coder:
Name: Age: Msn: Skype: Experience: Position: Why do you want to join?
GFX Deigner:
Name: Age: Msn: Skype: Position: Some of your work:
Source Coder:
Name: Age: Msn: Skype: Experience: Position: Why do you want to join?
Thank you for your time. We would love if u suggest anything u would like to see. :D Msn: fmcomar@hotmail.com [center][img]http://img828.imageshack.us/img828/3142/creditsjf.jpg[/img][/center] -Me -Sanity -I Vain I
